sentences.english: Rubins bet earned Goldman many multiples of Blacks salary.
sentences.chinese: 魯賓的豪賭爲高盛帶來的收入是布萊克薪水的好幾倍。

sentences.english: The city of foreign stock is filled with rate is very low, least only severalfold.
sentences.chinese: 國外股票的市盈率很低，最少的只有幾倍。

sentences.english: He's deserved to be punished several times, but I've forborne from doing so.
sentences.chinese: 他應受幾倍於此的處罰，但我忍住了，沒有這麼做。

sentences.english: The meeting room is some times larger than our classroom.
sentences.chinese: 那個會議室比我們的教室大幾倍。

sentences.english: But Fairey has been arrested several times for making his art.
sentences.chinese: 但費爾雷被逮捕他的藝術製作好幾倍。

sentences.english: There radon concentrations will severalfold to hundred times increasing when using spring water in the hotel rooms.
sentences.chinese: 氡濃度比沒有使用溫泉水時高出幾倍甚至幾百倍。

sentences.english: When we eat meat, we would be killing a corresponding multifold amount of plants.
sentences.chinese: 如果食肉，我們將會殺死相應好幾倍的植物。

sentences.english: Choose a foreground image size that is a larger multiple of your movie image tile size.
sentences.chinese: 選擇一個比您的影片圖像貼片大幾倍的前景圖像。

sentences.english: Japan would need a large multiple of the few immigrants it has at present.
sentences.chinese: 目前，日本還需要幾倍於當前的移民。

sentences.english: The actual figure is likely several fold higher due to under-reporting.
sentences.chinese: 當然，這一數字也有可能被人爲誇大了好幾倍。

sentences.english: The price is meant to be a multiple of this number.
sentences.chinese: 購買價將會是這個數字的好幾倍。
